Ni motozuite                     - ఆధారంగా (ādhāraṅgā)                     - Facts, data, stories, or evidence.
Ni shitagatte                    - ప్రకారం (prakāraṃ)                        - Rules, laws, plans, or instructions.
Ni yoru to / Ni yotte            - బట్టి (baṭṭi)                              - Observations, guesses, or what you heard.
Ni motozuku                      - ప్రాతిపదికన (prātipadikana)               - Formal grounds, legal basis, or principles.
Ni yotte / De                    - మూలంగా (mūlaṅgā)                       - Causes, reasons, or results of an event.
Daibuchigau                      - చాలా తేడా (Chālā tēḍā)                   - Greatly different, a big difference, or quite different.
